{"tid":1754770,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[馬愉生出嚟呀！] 深水埗碧匯選區馬愉生大炒民主黨幾多票？","createTime":"2019-11-25T10:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T09:37:52.000Z","uid":7439,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a7dfdd8e96cb9fe5eea048df1fd1a319876a825d","tid":1754770,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0HlCgnWF2L8Lse40/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0HlCgnWF2L8Lse40%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a2061ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.民主黨 鄒穎恒<br />\n1,462票 54%<br />\n2.經民聯 黃永威<br />\n1,150票 42%<br />\n3.普羅政治學苑 馬愉生<br />\n120票 4%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0JN3vCLv5bQ?t=153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0JN3vCLv5bQ%3Ft%3D153&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=b65f9098\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0JN3vCLv5bQ?t=153</a>"},{"pid":"5d8419c85655614b84e54754c8dd342e1576a82b","tid":1754770,"uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"談到和民主派撞區，馬愉生自言，「又想話我收共產黨錢？有就真係話我聽呀！」他解釋，參選「碧匯」是因為該區屬於新區，選民人口基數較少。<span style=\"color: red;\">「攞800到1,000票就贏。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>根據選舉事務處的官方資料，「碧匯」的選民數字為3,495人，屬深水埗25個選區中最少。<br />\n<br />\n對於黃毓民「派人鎅票」的說法，馬愉生斷然否認，稱認識對方多年，「佢敢做敢認，如果真係派我嚟，就直接支持我啦！」但他透露，已通知黃毓民有關參選一事，對方回覆稱，「好，去，無問題。」此外，馬愉生亦開門見山，指真正落區的時間為今年9月，「我話要落區，其實講咗一年，絕對唔存在鎅票，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你估十個提名易嫁？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"b8122fb721cf228024aeeb0df157c4fb5464bd8b","tid":1754770,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6073031d520c91b7cf18f341c6b5679aa1e771ee","tid":1754770,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0